data.value: Github page: https://github.com/Noisec/ | Checkbox: If you check that one button, the next time you launch the app, it will not be visible and will auto start the simulation. To uncheck it, just delete the config.ini file. | Trackbar: It controls the frequency of the process checking (to see if a simulated process has stopped running | min:1sec max:60sec). | Register button: It creates registry keys that only virtual machines have. | Unregister button: It deletes those keys.
